Package it.polimi.ingsw.network.server

Class ServerSideVisitor

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.network.server.ServerSideVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
NotificationVisitor
public class ServerSideVisitor extends Object implements NotificationVisitor
This class is used by the GameController to handle a message sent by the client. It implements visitor pattern to dispatch a Notification and apply different action to the model
